{{!
    @template block_smartedu/results

    Template to display list of discussions of a forum.

    Context variables required for this template:
    * has_error (boolean): Indicates if there was an error processing the forum.
    * error_message (string): The error message to display if `has_error` is true.
    * discussions (array): List of discussions in the forum, where each discussion contains:
        - name (string): The name of the discussion.
        - content (string): The content of the discussion.

    Example context (json):
    {
    }
}}
<div class="container">
    {{#has_error}}
        <div class="alert alert-danger" role="alert">
            {{{error_message}}}
        </div>
    {{/has_error}}

    {{^has_error}}
        {{#discussions}}
            <div class="card mt-2">
                <div class="card-header">
                    <strong>{{name}}</strong>
                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    {{content}}
                </div>
            </div>
        {{/discussions}}
    {{/has_error}}
</div>